96
00:06:48,699 --> 00:06:50,660
Sakura will never come back
to this nightlife world.

97
00:06:51,828 --> 00:06:54,872
Because she's the beloved lover of
the underboss of the Oya syndicate.

98
00:07:02,672 --> 00:07:04,590
