107
00:07:40,042 --> 00:07:42,295
So, why am I here?

108
00:07:44,672 --> 00:07:46,424
I was a little bit worried.

109
00:07:52,221 --> 00:07:53,681
You and Mr. Oya...

110
00:07:56,142 --> 00:07:57,602
How are you getting along?

111
00:08:00,646 --> 00:08:04,650
I know that he's a gentleman,
although he lives in that rough world.

112
00:08:05,902 --> 00:08:08,738
But I was concerned about you.

113
00:08:10,406 --> 00:08:13,409
Well, I'm glad that you're happy with him.

114
00:08:23,169 --> 00:08:25,004
Why do you look surprised?

115
00:08:26,380 --> 00:08:29,884
I've never talked about Mr. Oya

116
00:08:30,301 --> 00:08:32,637
with anybody else like this.

117
00:08:34,222 --> 00:08:37,475
And I don't intend to tell anyone.

118
00:08:38,267 --> 00:08:41,604
But having someone who knows about us

119
00:08:42,271 --> 00:08:43,189
kind of...

120
00:08:44,690 --> 00:08:46,526
makes me feel more courageous.

121
00:08:52,365 --> 00:08:53,366
Listen.

122
00:08:54,825 --> 00:08:55,993
Just because I know...

123
00:08:59,413 --> 00:09:02,500
doesn't mean
I support your relationship with him.

124
00:09:06,546 --> 00:09:07,463
Yes.

125
00:09:08,589 --> 00:09:09,924
Thank you.

126
00:09:23,646 --> 00:09:25,982
Can I have a drink too?

127
00:09:26,065 --> 00:09:27,233
Of course, come in.

128
00:09:28,150 --> 00:09:30,945
Thank you for patronizing my bar.

129
00:09:31,028 --> 00:09:32,029
Thanks.

130
00:09:33,614 --> 00:09:35,116
