131
00:09:35,741 --> 00:09:37,326
He has a distinct air about him.

132
00:09:37,577 --> 00:09:40,037
Sorry to interrupt, young lady.

133
00:09:40,121 --> 00:09:41,038
Huh?

134
00:09:41,872 --> 00:09:44,959
I interrupted your little meeting.

135
00:09:45,334 --> 00:09:46,877
Let me buy you a drink as an apology.

136
00:09:46,961 --> 00:09:48,421
No, you don't have to.

137
00:09:48,504 --> 00:09:50,756
You should take him up on his kind offer.

138
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:51,841
Umm...

139
00:09:54,844 --> 00:09:56,178
I'll go lock the door.

140
00:09:57,305 --> 00:09:58,306
What?

141
00:10:00,266 --> 00:10:01,684
Not so fast!

142
00:10:01,934 --> 00:10:03,686
You just got two more customers.

143
00:10:04,770 --> 00:10:05,730
You guys again.

144
00:10:06,856 --> 00:10:09,233
We're coming in, ready or not.

145
00:10:09,734 --> 00:10:12,028
Why are you here?

146
00:10:12,111 --> 00:10:14,655
We don't need you to protect my bar.

147
00:10:15,239 --> 00:10:17,116
I've told you that many times already.

148
00:10:17,199 --> 00:10:18,534
Don't you know, Ma'am?

149
00:10:19,452 --> 00:10:21,954
This area is not safe these days.

150
00:10:22,038 --> 00:10:24,582
Yes. I can give you an example...

151
00:10:30,755 --> 00:10:33,799
Bad guys doing things like this
are pretty rampant.

152
00:10:34,300 --> 00:10:36,010
We're not like that, mind you.

153
00:10:36,886 --> 00:10:38,471
What we're doing is just...

154
00:10:40,264 --> 00:10:42,933
telling you what could happen.

155
00:10:47,521 --> 00:10:48,648
Hey, stop it already--

156
00:10:49,231 --> 00:10:51,734
If you don't stop, I'll call the police!

157
00:10:51,817 --> 00:10:54,195
Don't ruin this precious bar of hers!

158
00:10:57,490 --> 00:10:58,616
Keep quiet!

159
00:10:58,699 --> 00:11:00,701
I said, stop!

160
00:11:11,796 --> 00:11:13,005
Come now!

161
00:11:13,089 --> 00:11:15,424
-Oww!
-Hey!

162
00:11:15,633 --> 00:11:18,260
Are you all right?

163
00:11:18,344 --> 00:11:19,887
Oww.

164
00:11:21,681 --> 00:11:23,724
Why you...

165
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:25,768
Take this!

166
00:11:31,816 --> 00:11:33,150
