188
00:12:51,312 --> 00:12:52,730
Don't be reckless like that.

189
00:12:53,647 --> 00:12:54,815
I'm sorry.

190
00:12:56,776 --> 00:12:57,943
Young lady.

191
00:12:59,820 --> 00:13:02,948
I asked her to bring you here today,

192
00:13:03,657 --> 00:13:05,701
so I could meet you.

193
00:13:06,994 --> 00:13:09,163
