200
00:13:38,818 --> 00:13:41,612
I'm saying it for your own good.

201
00:13:48,327 --> 00:13:49,453
I'm scared.

202
00:13:51,205 --> 00:13:52,122
But...

203
00:13:55,125 --> 00:13:57,211
I can't break up with him.

204
00:13:58,629 --> 00:14:00,589
That's impossible.

205
00:14:05,678 --> 00:14:07,263
When I'm with Mr. Oya,

206
00:14:08,848 --> 00:14:10,099
there's danger involved

207
00:14:11,350 --> 00:14:12,518
and I worry a lot.

208
00:14:14,395 --> 00:14:16,272
But I chose to be with him.

209
00:14:18,524 --> 00:14:20,359
All I can think of

210
