226
00:16:10,052 --> 00:16:12,972
See you again, Ma'am.
I'll have that drink next time.

227
00:16:19,520 --> 00:16:20,688
Wait here.

228
00:16:31,573 --> 00:16:33,075
Welcome back, sir.

229
00:16:33,158 --> 00:16:34,451
-Welcome back, sir.
-Welcome back, sir.

230
00:16:34,535 --> 00:16:36,078
