266
00:19:27,124 --> 00:19:28,876
My voice and my body were trembling

267
00:19:29,626 --> 00:19:31,587
in front of the boss.

268
00:19:33,881 --> 00:19:36,425
Mr. Oya, I...

269
00:19:38,177 --> 00:19:40,012
